Class SAT4jSolver

  • java.lang.Object

      • eshmun.modelrepair.sat.SAT4jSolver

  • public class SAT4jSolver
extends AbstractSatSolver
    This is the interface for the sat4j sat solver that is a java implementation for satisfiability problem.

      • SAT4jSolver

        public SAT4jSolver(AbstractExpression cnfExpression)
            throws NotCNFException,
                   org.sat4j.reader.ParseFormatException,
                   java.io.IOException
        Create a new SAT4J solver for the given problem.
        Parameters:
        cnfExpression - the expression to SAT solve.
        Throws:
        NotCNFException - if the expression is not in CNF format.
        org.sat4j.reader.ParseFormatException - if the expression is not in CNF format.
        java.io.IOException - if an error while reading problem occurred.
